# Prisma conventions

- Keep `DATABASE_URL` in `backend/.env` (see `backend/.env.example`).
- Keep `DATABASE_URL` in `apps/backend/.env` (see `apps/backend/.env.example`).
- Migrations are created via `npm run prisma:migrate:dev` inside `apps/backend/`.
- Add new models incrementally; avoid breaking renames without a migration plan.

